sequenceDiagram
    actor Developer
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant Wrapper as Codex dev wrapper
    participant Panel as SDD visual panel
    participant API as Bridge backend
    participant Files as Current project SDD files
    participant Feedback as Feedback service
    participant Codex as Codex action layer

    Developer->>App: Open app with CODEX_BRIDGE_DEV_MODE=true
    App->>Wrapper: Show dev wrapper
    Wrapper->>Panel: Open current-project SDD dashboard
    Panel->>API: GET /sdd/project?workspace_path=...
    API->>Files: Read allowed SDD files
    Files-->>API: Constitution, specs, tasks, diagrams
    API-->>Wrapper: Read-only SDD snapshot
    Wrapper-->>Panel: Render project-local architecture view
    Developer->>Panel: Mark diagram or app feedback
    Panel->>Feedback: Store feedback with SDD metadata
    Developer->>Panel: Request Codex update
    Panel->>Codex: Send workspace, SDD path, and selection context
    Codex-->>Panel: Return action status
